longBusinessSummary: Gatling Exploration Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of mineral properties in Canada. The company holds 100% interest in the Larder Lake Lake Project, a gold deposit that comprises patented and unpatented claims, leases, and mining licenses of 3,370 hectares located within the McVittie and McGarry townships in Ontario, Canada. Gatling Exploration Inc. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
